{
  "stem": "7358.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And again, there was some single young man that didn't have anybody.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my uncle took him along with us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was a very long journey, because we were going on one of the Russian trains.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was a supplementary type train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So every time when major trains were coming, we were put on a side, on a side railing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Sometimes we waited two, three days till we got permission to move again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But slowly, surely we arrived to a city called [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Beuthen. ?] This city was-- belonged to German, to Germany, prior to the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But when they readjusted the borders, when Ukraine was given back to the Russians, a portion of Germany was given to the Poles as compensation for the land they ceded to, to the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We came to [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Beuthen. ?] And the town was full of Jewish refugees coming from all over the place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My uncle managed to rent an apartment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he did a little business.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I don't know exactly what it was doing exactly-- was buying and selling things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And it was very fashionable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "People used to travel to Germany, because after the war, they were also devastated.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And for food, they used to exchange clothes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They would bring food to Germany and in return get personal possessions, watches and clothes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So it was that type of business going on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And a lot of people were doing business that way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The war was over where we were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the war still continued further out, deep into Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But in our area, for all intents and purposes--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--the war was over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I discovered that they have Jewish youth organizations in town.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
